[99.500217, "o", "✅ SUCCESS! The fix correctly handles the DST transition.\r\n   The maintenance window reminder will now be sent at the correct time.\r\n\r\nThe bug was: BERLIN_TZ.localize(utc_dt) treated UTC time as Berlin time.\r\nThe fix is: UTC_TZ.localize(utc_dt).astimezone(BERLIN_TZ) properly converts.\r\n============================================================\r\n"]
